headline: Xcel Energy Powering More of the Economy as Energy Transition Continues
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, June 05, 2025--Xcel Energy is powering even more of the economy as it continues to reduce the carbon emissions from its operations, the company announced in its 20th annual Sustainability Report today.

headline: Xcel Energy provides update on Ten Mile Creek Solar Project to St. Croix County officials
summary: EAU CLAIRE - During a recent meeting with St. Croix County officials, Xcel Energy provided a comprehensive update on the Ten Mile Creek Solar Project, highlighting a number of significant milestones...
